quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  15,26,"Twararemye ikiremwa muntu tumukuye mw’ivu ryumutse rifise n’ijwi, rivuye muvyondo vyirabura vyavunditswe"
  15,27,"N’ibisigo twabiremye imbere yaho, mu muriro w’umuyaga w’ubushuhe bwinshi cane"
  15,28,"N’Umuremyi wawe igihe yabwira Abamarayika biwe ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nzorema umuntu ndamukuye mw’ivu ryumutse rifise ijwi rivuye muvyondo vyirabura bivunditswe"
  15,29,"Ninaheza kumurema nukumuhuheramwo umutima uvuye iwanje, rero nimu murweko nukumu gamburukira"
  15,30,Rero abamarayika bose hamwe bara gamburuka
  15,31,Dukuyemwo uwitwa Ibilisi niwe yanse kuba hamwe naba gamburutse
  15,32,"Imana yavuze iti:- ewe Ibilisi vyabaye gute kutabaye hamwe naba gamburutse"
  15,33,"Shetani imwishura iti:- jewe sinshobora kugamburukira umuntu waremye mw’ivu ryumutse rifise ijwi rivuye muvyondo bivunze"
  15,34,"Imana ivuga iti:- nuve ngaho mugihe wirukanywe nukuba kure y’imigisha yose"
  15,35,Kandi mu vy’ukuri bizoba kuri wewe harimwo umuvumo kugeza k’umusi w’imperuka
  15,36,"Shetani yishura iti:- Muremyi wanje numpe umwanya kugeza k’umusi bazozurwa abantu bose"
  15,37,"Imana yishura iti:- mu vy’ukuri wewe uri mubaronse ikibanza"
  15,38,Kugeza k’umusi w’umwanya wagenewe ushitse niho uzosandaba
  15,39,"Nayo yishura iti:- Muremyi wanje kubera yuko wanciriye urubanza rw’ukuzimira, nanje nzobaryosha ryosha aba bantu kuri iy’Isi nze ndabazimize bose"
  15,40,Dukuyemwo abantu bawe beranda bisukuye neza naneza
  15,41,"Imana ivuga iti:- iyi nzira yabo niyukuza iwanje kandi igororotse"
  15,42,"Mu vy’ukuri abantu banje, wewe ntabushobozi uzoba ufise kuribo, atari bamwe bagukurikira muri abo bazimiye"
  15,43,Kandi ntankeka umuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu nibwo bwicaro bwabo bemerewe bose
  15,44,"Uwo muriro ufise imiryango indwi, no kumuryango umw’umwe hariho ahantu hagabuwe"